Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,填補最討厭和最喜歡產生的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個人的推理和懸疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看穿困難案件的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.30,0:00:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妃和檢察官 法庭對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 溫泉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經很久沒去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個時候 楓葉也紅了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我推薦去這家露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這裡的溫泉對皮膚特別好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽妳也應該偶爾放下工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去休假一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.60,0:02:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栗山小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下個月我的日程上都有些什麼安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.10,0:02:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我記得手頭上的案子預計下周開庭宣判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是當番怎麼辦的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎 還有那個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我把資料拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.60,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當番是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.60,0:02:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 為了那些沒錢請律師的被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國家幫他們出錢請律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒人願意為他們辯護的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由律師協會來決定當番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.40,0:02:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是大略地看了一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒人接這個案子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告也完全有可能打贏這場官司的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是對手不好對付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對手是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子的負責人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九條檢察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官的瑪丹娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.40,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭的對決Ⅱ 妃VS九條（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.10,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢 這次就說工作繁忙把這案子推掉算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妃律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼樣的案子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個多月前的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在杯戶町的一幢大樓的事務所裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了那家公司社長的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從室內留下來的指紋和物品來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手像是一個盜竊大樓的慣犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且有前科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.50,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這件案子沒必要開庭審理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著公司沒人就溜進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果被死者發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人爭吵後動起手來 被告都承認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是起訴的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是以竊盜及謀殺罪起訴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謀殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種情況不應該是過失殺人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 九條檢察官應該不會犯這樣的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.20,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栗山小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官的刑事報告書和口供都有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事件調查報告還沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請去要一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有解剖報告也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉就下次再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)\pos(320,470)\fs36\fsp2}東京拘留所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再確認一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發當晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.10,0:04:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,450)\pos(242,324)\fs30}井上隆志(55歲)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.10,0:04:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,450)\pos(234,350)\fs20}犯罪嫌疑人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你撬開位於野本大廈2樓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大津不動產事務所的窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潛入事務所內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在事務所裡尋找財物的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當你正要打開社長室裡的保險箱的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被偶然進入的社長大津敏之發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆在扭打的過程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抓起旁邊的玻璃煙灰缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猛擊他的頭部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導致他的死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方說錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保險箱裡的錢你怎麼處理了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是根據職員的證詞說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當天不動產交易入帳的1200萬現金不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方認為你在殺了大津社長之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開保險箱把錢拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確在你的住宅裡沒找到錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是保險箱的鎖上有你的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.90,0:05:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以警方懷疑你也不是沒有道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實沒有拿走那些錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那個傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.10,0:05:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前就認識死者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打了死者頭部幾下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一下嗎？ 還是兩下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然被人看見 我就慌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解剖報告上說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者頭部有三次被毆打的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三次打擊是致命傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打了一下還沒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩下 三下的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能被認為蓄意殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是跟你站在同一陣線的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是對自己不利的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要誠實地跟我說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再確認一次 你確實沒有想要殺害死者 是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.00,0:06:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開庭的時候就集中在這一點上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,380)\fs30}東京市法院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告 井上隆志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發當晚8點30分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撬開位於杯戶町3町目2-9的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,340)\fs24}不動產公司社長搶劫殺人事件 初審
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野本大廈2樓的大津不動產社長室的窗戶 潛入該公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在尋找室內財物的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被偶然進入的該公司社長大津敏之發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手用所持兇器威脅死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當死者打開保險箱門的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時用旁邊的玻璃煙灰缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猛擊死者頭部三次 導致其死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.10,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盜走了保險箱裡的現金1200萬元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.00,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據此 根據刑法第240條的竊盜謀殺罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求法庭判決被告無期徒刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告對於檢察官宣讀的控訴事實承認嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不認罪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.30,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是進去偷東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼是竊盜謀殺罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審判長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請講 辯護人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控訴事實認為他是竊盜謀殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是被告並沒有殺意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請判決為過失殺人罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說否認竊盜謀殺罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.50,0:08:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.40,0:08:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該用第240條第205項的過失殺人罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辯護人不同意檢察官的控訴事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有什麼意見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告選擇大津不動產作為竊盜對象的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是在大樓裡尋找目標的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然選擇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說只是為了竊盜而進去的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.80,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼對於大津不動產以及死者大津敏之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有任何仇恨的 對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九條檢察官到底想要說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審判長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白檢察官提問的意圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.10,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告知道遠藤紀子這個女人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會忘了自己的獨生女兒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨生女兒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和20年前離婚的前妻的獨生女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時只有8歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這和案子有什麼關係呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不回答我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官的問題中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涉及被告親人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能認為檢察官的意圖是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓被告的意志動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女兒和庭審有關嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤紀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大津不動產管理的另一棟大樓裡經營俱樂部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞她和死者大津敏之有曖昧關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.20,0:10:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說被告潛入案發的大樓並不是偶然的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.90,0:10:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有證詞證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告因為女兒的事情而怨恨死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.20,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不知道那傢伙的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 你問問她本人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就在旁聽席上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以出庭作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,324)\fs30}遠藤紀子(28歲)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,350)\fs20}井上隆志的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是瑪丹娜的秘密武器嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要的話可以請遠藤小姐出庭作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.20,0:10:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官說的事情都是真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被那個男人給騙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是讓我開店經營 還甜言蜜語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全被他利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳和妳父親什麼時候開始聯繫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前媽媽病死的時候開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候起 爸爸經常來我的店裡看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳跟他說了大津的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說要替我向大津要賠償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得事情變得越來越不利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.40,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 他有怨恨人家的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果又打了三下的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算說沒有殺意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有人會相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後 希望妳跟我說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認為妳爸爸會殺大津嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸雖然是個竊賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他是個不會殺人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.60,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的辯護看來會很艱難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你…又在睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在閉著眼睛思考問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰在睡覺啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想出來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫助媽媽的好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下這樣的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是英理這傢伙不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告有殺人動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還把指紋清清楚楚地留在保險箱的鎖上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼辯護啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼只有保險箱的鎖上面有指紋呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個 當然是戴著手套了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.80,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但開保險箱的時候 戴著手套礙事所以就脫掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候遇到死者 就用煙灰缸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.50,0:13:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 作為兇器的煙灰缸上也應該有指紋 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因為手套已經脫掉了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是煙灰缸上面沒有留下指紋呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是後來擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有用沾了油的抹布擦過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不把保險箱也一起擦了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.30,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了人匆忙逃跑時給忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.30,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是保險箱裡的錢是什麼時候被盜的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺人之後再次打開保險箱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是說匆忙逃跑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有什麼地方說不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.10,0:13:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是在做一些說不通的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊 這不是強詞奪理嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 小孩子給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 爸爸你去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 玩柏青哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)\pos(630,346)\an3\fs26}現場遺留品清單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)\pos(606,380)\an3}①玻璃煙灰缸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)\pos(630,410)\an3}②軍用手套一副
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)\pos(582,440)\an3}③眼鏡螺絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.18,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,830)\pos(582,470)\an3}④高爾夫球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到這裡來幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不 我只是有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想看看能不能幫助妃律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而來看現場的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你多嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來名偵探也非常悠閒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妃律師也是來調查現場的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在問管理員能不能看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(350,324)\fs28\fsp2}秋山拓也(56歲)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(335,350)\fs22}管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯伯 是你最先發現社長屍體的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的情況能不能跟我詳細說說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 那天晚上9點鐘左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在看棒球的電視轉播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.30,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有馬先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老頭…不 你有看見社長嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 8點去巡邏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事務所裡一個人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我從家裡出去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說要回事務所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他肯定是從緊急出口進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是事務所的門上了鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼叫都沒有人開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是在最裡面的社長室裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來給他送忘了的老花眼鏡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.30,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻煩你跟我一起上去開個門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個有馬先生是大津社長的女婿吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他在附近開了家義大利餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了鎖的就是這扇門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是用這把備用鑰匙開了門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 雅彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 有人在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在打人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙 快給我鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門的鑰匙只有社長有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你稍微讓開一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你振作點啊 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋山先生 快去叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就是出了事的社長室嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這扇門鎖著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門的鑰匙在有馬先生手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.30,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有馬先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.50,0:17:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是我剛才在電話裡說的妃律師以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你就是那個有名的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(460,326)\fs28\fsp2}有馬雅彥(35歲)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(460,350)\fs20}義大利餐廳經營者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有馬先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在百忙之中打擾你 真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看社長室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.60,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個房間現在沒有使用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.60,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 雖說警方已經准許使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了這樣的事情 爸爸死在這房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後這房間怎麼處置還不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是保持警方調查之後的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有馬先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者是倒在哪裡的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保險箱的前面 這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著頭倒在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是井上要打開保險箱的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被死者發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告一開始就是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是在這以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上用帶來的刀子什麼的威脅死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開保險箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 在保險箱打開的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用煙灰缸從背後猛擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是說被告在撒謊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慣犯經常如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不信任被告還怎麼辯護？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 妳還說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在瑪丹娜讓妳吃足苦頭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.00,0:19:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.00,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.50,0:19:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯伯 你是從那個小視窗看見兇手的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.90,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託再站在保險箱的前面一次讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你要幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在那裡等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 從這裡看過去被屏風給擋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也看不到叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋山先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…我看到的不是那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊牆上映出來的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牆上映出來的人影嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.20,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時房間裡面沒開燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從窗戶照射進來的霓虹燈光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上映出了正在打人的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.70,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是毆打大津社長的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就聽到大津社長倒下去的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再問你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.40,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你並沒有看見井上毆打死者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 律師小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這沒有多大不同吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手自己也說打過了 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 有馬先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見他本人在打人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和看見打人的人影是完全不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.00,0:21:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被告在判決下來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也只是嫌疑犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這麼悲慘的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪你們會如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.60,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個鐘停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.80,0:21:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是死去的社長在高爾夫球比賽中獲勝贏得的獎品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是作為紀念品裝飾房間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平時不用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.00,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有馬先生 請來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道保險箱密碼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.80,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了死者以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了 只有我爸爸知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說這也是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.30,0:21:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連會計也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲 不要妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.80,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個案子的伎倆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋山先生說他看見正在打什麼東西的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.90,0:22:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼東西倒下去的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這個小伎倆都是可以做出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 設計這個伎倆的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.20,0:23:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 店是蠻高級的 可是義大利麵卻做得不好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.90,0:23:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 橄欖油的味道太重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.70,0:23:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.70,0:24:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照叔叔的話重現了當晚的機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.40,0:24:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 難道說兇手是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.10,0:24:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 叔叔說他要在法庭上澄清一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.10,0:24:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.40,0:24:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法庭的對決Ⅱ 妃VS九條（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.80,0:24:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.80,0:24:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集解決案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.70,0:24:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 幫幫媽媽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.40,0:24:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九條檢察官真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.00,0:24:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.92,0:00:27.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們兩人所訴說的未來裡 就像有你在身邊的棲身地一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.10,0:00:31.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當作是你的全部喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.57,0:00:43.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信兩個人牽著的手 發誓我們一起走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.16,0:00:49.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“最討厭” 即使是謊言我也說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.91,0:00:56.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“最喜歡” 如果是謊言我就不會說喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.67,0:01:05.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法見面的時候 你就像無暇考慮其他東西一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.38,0:01:10.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的心裡只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.47,0:01:14.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.02,0:01:24.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓兩個愛永不分離 請緊緊擁抱對方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.28,0:01:31.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此不安的夜晚 還是會來臨的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.58,0:01:39.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}那時候 要緊緊地擁抱我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.09,0:22:40.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片星空如此燦爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.68,0:22:49.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你在其中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.36,0:23:00.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你在身旁 我不想變成獨自一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.87,0:23:10.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映入眼簾的事物 全都開始扭曲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.01,0:23:21.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望天空如此寬廣 群星如此閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.89,0:23:32.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻無法用手觸及 為什麼星空如此遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.49,0:23:37.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想見到你
